uently Asked Questions","faq_1_question":"Is Sorteo Pro free?","faq_1_answer":"Yes, Sorteo Pro is completely free to use for all your giveaways.","faq_2_question":"Can I save my settings?","faq_2_answer":"Yes, your theme settings are saved locally in your browser."},"WheelGeo":{"title":"Wheel of Names & Random Picker","description":"Looking for a <b>Wheel of Names</b>? Sorteo Pro includes a fully customizable <b>Random Name Picker Wheel</b> that is fair, free, and fun.","what_is_wheel":"What is a Wheel of Names?","what_is_wheel_answer":"A <b>Wheel of Names</b> is a digital tool that picks a random winner by spinning a virtual wheel. It is popularly used by teachers, influencers, and event organizers for <b>random selection</b>. Sorteo Pro upgrades this experience with cinematic effects.","features_list":"Advanced Wheel Features","feature_1":"100% Random & Fair","feature_2":"Custom Colors & Themes","feature_3":"No Ads / No Login","feature_4":"Sound Effects & Animation","feature_5":"Instant Result Verification","cta_button":"Try Wheel Mode Now","how_to_title":"How to create a Wheel of Names","how_to_step_1":"Enter the names of participants manually or paste a list from Excel/Text.","how_to_step_2":"Customize the wheel colors, spin duration, and sound effects in the 'Visual Editor'.","how_to_step_3":"Click 'Start Giveaway' to spin the wheel and pick a random winner.","how_to_step_4":"Share the official Certificate of Validity with your audience.","trust_link_text":"Learn about our Secure RNG"},"Glossary":{"title":"Giveaway Glossary","term_1":"Random Number Generator (RNG)","def_1":"An algorithm that generates a sequence of numbers or symbols that cannot be reasonably predicted better than by random chance. Sorteo Pro uses cryptographically secure RNG.","term_2":"Provably Fair","def_2":"A system that allows players to verify that the outcome of a game or raffle was generated correctly and was not manipulated by the operator.","term_3":"Instagram Comment Picker","def_3":