circle into segments representing participants and spins to select one at random.","learn_more":"Try {tool}","cta_title":"Ready to run a fair giveaway?","cta_button":"Start Giveaway"},"Versus":{"title":"The Best AppSorteos Alternative for Instagram (Free & Unlimited)","description":"Looking for an AppSorteos alternative? Sorteo Pro allows you to pick Instagram winners for free and without comment limits. 2024 Comparison.","header_tagline":"2025 Comparison","header_title_part1":"The Ultimate AppSorteos","header_title_part2":"Alternative","header_desc":"We analyze AppSorteos vs Sorteo Pro. Discover why thousands of users are switching.","direct_answer_title":"What is the best free alternative to AppSorteos?","direct_answer_text":"<strong>Sorteo Pro</strong> is the best <strong>free AppSorteos alternative</strong> for 2025. While AppSorteos forces you to pay for >1,000 comments, Sorteo Pro offers <strong>unlimited comments</strong>, <strong>no login requirements</strong>, and a verifiable <strong>Certificate of Validity</strong> — 100% free forever.","table":{"feature":"Feature","us":"Sorteo Pro","them":"AppSorteos / EasyPromos","row_price":"Price","row_price_us":"100% FREE","row_price_us_desc":"No subscriptions or tricks","row_price_them":"Paid / Freemium","row_price_them_desc":"Expensive for many comments","row_limits":"Comment Limit","row_limits_us":"UNLIMITED","row_limits_us_desc":"Load 10k+ comments","row_limits_them":"Limited / Paid","row_limits_them_desc":"Pay extra if over 1k","row_design":"Design & Animation","row_design_us":"Cinematic","row_design_us_desc":"Customizable and viral","row_design_them":"Basic","row_design_them_desc":"Static and boring","row_login":"Login","row_login_us":"Not Required","row_login_us_desc":"Start instantly","row_login_them":"Mandatory","row_login_them_desc":"Data required"},"why_us":{"title":"Why are we better than free EasyPromos alternatives?","p1":"Many creators look for 'free EasyPromos alternatives' because traditional tools h