nt Results","feature_3_desc":"Get your random numbers in milliseconds.","feature_4_title":"Mobile Friendly","feature_4_desc":"Works perfectly on any device.","how_to_title":"How to use the Random Number Generator","how_to_step_1":"Enter the list of numbers or options you want to randomize.","how_to_step_2":"Select the 'Slot Machine' style for a classic RNG look.","how_to_step_3":"Click 'Start Giveaway' to generate a random number.","how_to_step_4":"Share the verified result with your audience."},"RngPage":{"title":"Random Number Generator | Free & Secure RNG","description":"Generate random numbers instantly with Sorteo Pro. Free, secure, and customizable random number generator for games, lotteries, and scientific use.","faq_1_q":"Is this RNG truly random?","faq_1_a":"Yes, we use a cryptographically secure pseudo-random number generator (CSPRNG) which is the industry standard for fairness.","faq_2_q":"Is there a limit to how many numbers I can generate?","faq_2_a":"No, you can generate unlimited random numbers for free."},"ListRandomizerPage":{"title":"List Randomizer | Random Team Generator & Sorter","description":"The best free List Randomizer and Random Team Generator. Shuffle a list, pick a winner, or split items into random groups instantly. Secure & free.","h1":"Free List Randomizer & Team Generator","subtitle":"Shuffle lists, split teams, and pick items instantly.","faq_1_q":"How does the List Randomizer work?","faq_1_a":"We use a Fisher-Yates shuffle algorithm powered by cryptographically secure random numbers to ensure a truly random order.","faq_2_q":"Can I randomize names for a raffle?","faq_2_a":"Yes! Just paste your list of names, and the tool will pick a winner or shuffle the entire list."},"ListRandomizerGeo":{"direct_answer_title":"What is a List Randomizer & Team Generator?","direct_answer_text":"A <strong>List Randomizer</strong> is a tool that takes a list of items (names, numbers, or options) and rearranges them into a completely <strong>random order</strong>. It is essential for giveaways, <strong>random team generation</strong>, and unbiased sorting. <strong>Sorteo Pro</strong> offers a free, secure list randomizer with instant results.","cta_button":"Randomize List & Teams","feature_1_title":"Truly Random Shuffle","feature_1_desc":"Uses secure algorithms to ensure no bias in the order.","feature_2_title":"Random Team Generator","feature_2_desc":"Perfect for splitting groups into random teams or pairs.","feature_3_title":"Bulk Input","feature_3_desc":"Paste thousands of items instantly.","feature_4_title":"Visual Verification","feature_4_desc":"See the randomization happen in real-time.","how_to_title":"How to randomize a list","how_to_step_1":"Enter the list of names, items, or numbers you want to shuffle.","how_to_step_2":"Choose the 'Grid' or 'List' view from the Visual Editor.","how_to_step_3":"Click 'Start Giveaway' to randomize the order instantly.","how_to_step_4":"Use the result to form teams, assign tasks, or pick a winner."},"YesNoPage":{"title":"Yes or No Wheel | Random Decision Maker","description":"Spin the Yes or No Wheel to make a random decision. Free, fair, and fun way to decide. Flip a coin style wheel.","h1":"Yes or No Wheel","option_yes":"YES","option_no":"NO"},"YesNoGeo":{"title":"Yes or No Wheel","what_is_title":"What is a Yes or No Wheel?","what_is_answer":"A <b>Yes or No Wheel</b> is a simple random decision tool. It works like flipping a coin but with a visual spinning wheel. <b>Sorteo Pro</b> provides a fair, 50/50 chance for every spin using secure RNG.","features_list":"Wheel Features","feature_1":"Simple Yes/No","feature_2":"No Ads","feature_3":"Secure RNG","feature_4":"Customizable","feature_5":"Instant Result","cta_button":"Spin for Answer","trust_link_text":"Learn about our Randomness","how_to_title":"How to use the Yes or No Wheel","how_to_step_1":"The wheel is already set up with 'YES' and 'NO' options.","how_to_step_2":"Click 'Start Giveaway' to spin the wheel.","how_to_